						               													<description>The Emotions family loves to tell stories. Every night, little Joy and her sister Sadness get together with uncle Anger, uncle Fear and their cousin Disgust and tell each other wonderful stories: can you guess which story each of them is telling? Beware: if you attribute the story to the wrong narrator, the Emotions family may take offence and... make you lose the game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A game for the whole family, who have to work together to guess which of the tales depicted on the playing cards is being told by a different member of the Emotions family.&amp;#10;The active player draws an Emotion card and must decide which of the five Fairy Tale cards in play best represents it, voting for it in secret. The other players confront each other and try to guess which card has been chosen.&amp;#10;The aim of the game is to finish all the Emotion cards without ever choosing a Fairy Tale card marked with a Flame.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
